YahooMeteoImplementation - Class in appsgate.lig.meteo.yahoo
Implementation of Yahoo forecast, allows to change unit (Celsius,Fahrenheit) but gives maximum 2 days forecast, as input its required the WOEID (http://developer.yahoo.com/geo/geoplanet/guide/concepts.html#hierarchy) which indicates the location for the forecast.
